{"content":"<p>Implementing <mark>internationalization</mark> in the theme only requires some simple configurations.</p>\n<p>Let's take an example of creating a project with <strong>Chinese</strong> as the default language and including <strong>English</strong> and <strong>French</strong>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"directory-structure\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#directory-structure\"><span>Directory Structure</span></a></h2>\n<p>First, you need to create a directory structure similar to the following:</p>\n<div class=\"vp-file-tree\"><ul>\n<FileTreeItem type=\"folder\" :expanded=\"true\" :empty=\"false\"><span class=\"tree-node folder\"><VPIcon name=\"vscode-icons:folder-type-docs\"></VPIcon><span class=\"name\">docs</span></span>\n<ul>\n<FileTreeItem type=\"folder\" :expanded=\"true\" :empty=\"false\"><span class=\"tree-node folder\"><VPIcon name=\"vscode-icons:default-folder\"></VPIcon><span class=\"name focus\"><strong>en</strong></span><span class=\"comment\">  # English directory</span></span>\n<ul>\n<FileTreeItem type=\"file\" :expanded=\"false\" :empty=\"true\"><span class=\"tree-node file\"><VPIcon name=\"vscode-icons:file-type-markdown\"></VPIcon><span class=\"name\">foo.md</span></span></FileTreeItem>\n<FileTreeItem type=\"file\" :expanded=\"false\" :empty=\"true\"><span class=\"tree-node file\"><VPIcon name=\"flat-color-icons:info\"></VPIcon><span class=\"name\">README.md</span><span class=\"comment\"> # English home page</span></span></FileTreeItem>\n</ul>\n</FileTreeItem>\n<FileTreeItem type=\"folder\" :expanded=\"true\" :empty=\"false\"><span class=\"tree-node folder\"><VPIcon name=\"vscode-icons:default-folder\"></VPIcon><span class=\"name focus\"><strong>fr</strong></span><span class=\"comment\">  # French directory</span></span>\n<ul>\n<FileTreeItem type=\"file\" :expanded=\"false\" :empty=\"true\"><span class=\"tree-node file\"><VPIcon name=\"vscode-icons:file-type-markdown\"></VPIcon><span class=\"name\">foo.md</span></span></FileTreeItem>\n<FileTreeItem type=\"file\" :expanded=\"false\" :empty=\"true\"><span class=\"tree-node file\"><VPIcon name=\"flat-color-icons:info\"></VPIcon><span class=\"name\">README.md</span><span class=\"comment\"> # French home page</span></span></FileTreeItem>\n</ul>\n</FileTreeItem>\n<FileTreeItem type=\"file\" :expanded=\"false\" :empty=\"true\"><span class=\"tree-node file\"><VPIcon name=\"vscode-icons:file-type-markdown\"></VPIcon><span class=\"name\">foo.md</span></span></FileTreeItem>\n<FileTreeItem type=\"file\" :expanded=\"false\" :empty=\"true\"><span class=\"tree-node file\"><VPIcon name=\"flat-color-icons:info\"></VPIcon><span class=\"name\">README.md</span><span class=\"comment\"> # Chinese home page</span></span></FileTreeItem>\n</ul>\n</FileTreeItem>\n</ul>\n</div><p>Here, <code v-pre>docs/en/</code> is used to store <strong>English</strong> documents, <code v-pre>docs/fr/</code> stores <strong>French</strong> documents, and <strong>Chinese</strong> documents are stored directly under <code v-pre>docs/</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"hint-container important\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">Consistent directory and file names across languages</p>\n<p>Try to keep the file names and directory names consistent across different language directories. This helps the theme correctly navigate to different language versions of the article when switching languages.</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"vuepress-configuration\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#vuepress-configuration\"><span>VuePress Configuration</span></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"default-language\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#default-language\"><span>Default Language</span></a></h3>\n<p>In <code v-pre>.vuepress/config.ts</code>, declare the default language:</p>\n<CodeTabs id=\"84\" :data='[{\"id\":\".vuepress/config.ts\"}]'><template #title0=\"{ value, isActive }\"><VPIcon name=\"vscode-icons:file-type-typescript\"/><span>.vuepress/config.ts</span></template><template #tab0=\"{ value, isActive }\"><div class=\"language-ts line-numbers-mode\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"ts\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\"><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark has-diff vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">import</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> {</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> defineUserConfig</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> }</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\"> from</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> '</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">vuepress</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">export</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\"> default</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> defineUserConfig</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">({</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">  // Declare the default language</span></span>\n<span class=\"line diff add\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">  lang</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">: </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">zh-CN</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">, </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">  // Locales supported under multilingual</span></span>\